Peninsula Software of Virginia, Inc. (PenSoft) manufactures payroll software designed specifically to help small to mid-sized businesses and payroll service providers process virtually any payroll and related tax requirements faster, easier, and more cost effectively.PenSoft is committed to providing the best value available in payroll software, backed by program support unsurpassed in the industry. Our sophisticated, comprehensive software packages make one of the most complex, time-consuming tasks employers face as simple as a few keystrokes.

PenSoft relies largely on distributors, customer referrals, and the internet to continue the company's rapid growth. PenSoft has grown to support thousands of clients with a highly trained staff of degreed accountants, computer programmers, program support consultants, and business experts.
